a heck of
a lot of money here.

128
00:05:36,034 --> 00:05:37,655
Ed, it's
not just about money.

129
00:05:37,724 --> 00:05:40,344
No, well, I'm-- No, I'm trying
to understand, that's all.

130
00:05:41,689 --> 00:05:44,965
